## v1.0.0 (2026-01-04)

**Initial version.** Documents the JSON-stdout-vs-stderr rate-limit-parsing bug discovered in ProjectScylla PR #126. Established the pattern of parsing the error message field from `is_error: true` JSON before falling back to stderr.
